title: Snow Removal Kit for Cars and Trucks with Scraper, Shovel and Brush
description: Be prepared for winter emergencies anywhere with this shovel, brush and scraper kit. The shovel kit for cars and trucks features an anodized aluminum handle with a polypropylene grip as well as a polypropylene shovel blade, scraper and brush. Plus, keep everything together in the convenient carrying bag that is portable and will fit in any vehicle.
